<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/5200478600/JgjQuFNAd?from=page_1006065200478600_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime">上海迪士尼将实行预约新规</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359306" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/005FWG36gy1ghg10ls2x8j31900u0qv7.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/005FWG36gy1ghg10ls2x8j31900u0qv7.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/005FWG36gy1ghg10ls2x8j31900u0qv7-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/005FWG36gy1ghg10ls2x8j31900u0qv7-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>因国家文化和旅游部下发《关于推进旅游企业扩大复工复业有关事项的通知》，调整旅游景区限量由最大承载量的 30％调至 50％，上海迪士尼乐园也正逐渐增加其日承载量。</p>
<p>从 2020 年 8 月 24 日起，乐园将实行预约新规。持乐园年卡或非指定日票的游客，将可在符合其所持年卡或门票类别的任意适用入园日期到访乐园 。所有其他游客可购买包括当日在内的乐园指定日票入园游玩（视门票库存而定）。不过，所有游客仍需在到乐园主入口提交相关个人信息，获取预约码。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/8/supreme-fall-winter-2020-accessories">Supreme 又出了什么奇怪配件？</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359307" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme-fall-winter-2020-accessories-9.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme-fall-winter-2020-accessories-9.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme-fall-winter-2020-accessories-9-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme-fall-winter-2020-accessories-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme-fall-winter-2020-accessories-9-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，Supreme 的配件系列的产品通常都让人意想不到。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359308" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme.jpg" alt="" width="2113" height="861" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme.jpg 2113w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme-360x147.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme-768x313.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/supreme-1024x417.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2113px) 100vw, 2113px" /></p>
<p>最近，Supreme 发布了 2020 年秋冬新品，配件系列中比较特别的包括了电玩街机、口红、篮球、透明鱼缸、牙膏、以及和恐怖电影《Chucky》合作的布娃娃等。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.ototodesign.com/collections/all-products/products/vino-corkscrew-and-bottle-opener">拍拍翅膀，开瓶红酒</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359309" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/grab-the-wine-dont-hold-back-1800-5f3509d68a7bd.jpg" alt="" width="1115" height="650" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/grab-the-wine-dont-hold-back-1800-5f3509d68a7bd.jpg 1115w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/grab-the-wine-dont-hold-back-1800-5f3509d68a7bd-360x210.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/grab-the-wine-dont-hold-back-1800-5f3509d68a7bd-768x448.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/grab-the-wine-dont-hold-back-1800-5f3509d68a7bd-1024x597.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1115px) 100vw, 1115px" /></p>
<p>以色列设计工作室 OTOTO 设计了一款蝙蝠形的开瓶器，定价 24 美元（约人民币 167 元）。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359311" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/bat.gif" alt="" width="500" height="286" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/bat.gif 500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/bat-360x206.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>
<p>当用户扭动蝙蝠脑袋开瓶时，蝙蝠的翅膀还会随之摆动。除了能用来开红酒，蝙蝠的「小牙齿」也能用来撬开啤酒盖。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%9C%88%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%88%A0%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E4%BA%86%23&amp;Refer=top">微信朋友圈可以删评论了</a></h4>
<p>iOS 版微信更新到最新 7.0.15 版本后，可以删除朋友圈评论了。如果评论你的人，也用最新版微信，被删除评论后再看回你这条朋友圈，原评论位置会提示「评论已被删除」，其他人看不到该提示。不过，删除评论后，对方不会收到消息提醒。</p>
<p>网友：「删除评论和拉黑对方有什么区别？」「我需要的是重新编辑的功能。」「逐渐 QQ 化。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357580" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed.png" alt="" width="1029" height="165" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-360x58.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-768x123.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1024x164.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>没灵感了？来看一把椅子能多好玩</h4>
<h4><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u01979pstld" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></h4>
<p>日本设计公司 Nendo 以漫画设计语言为灵感，将一张普通的椅子结构重组，赋予每一张椅子鲜活的个性。</p>
<p>更好玩的是，后来他们还把这些椅子都从二次元带到<a href="http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/50-manga-chairs/50-manga-chairs-3/?egenre">现实世界了</a>。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359317" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/50_manga_chairs_in_Milan_05_takumi_ota.jpg" alt="" width="820" height="547" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/50_manga_chairs_in_Milan_05_takumi_ota.jpg 820w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/50_manga_chairs_in_Milan_05_takumi_ota-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/50_manga_chairs_in_Milan_05_takumi_ota-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px" /></p>
➜荣耀 X10 ：5G 手机，千元拐点
https://www.ifanr.com/1338432?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	16220
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338460" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>如果说 3 月 4 月的手机市场是以旗舰机发布为主的话，那么 5 月手机发布的主题就是出货中坚机了。而在前天荣耀智慧全场景发布会之后，荣耀手机产品线中的 X 系列也在今日得到更新。有所不同的是，曾经作为后缀的 X 如今前进一步，成为了前缀，也就有了荣耀 X10 这款新机。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338456" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-08-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-08-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-08-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-08-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-08.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>与今年业界惯用的挖坑屏不同，这一次荣耀 X10 依旧沿用了升降摄像头的设计。好处当然显而易见：正面屏幕的观感更加完整。与之对应的，荣耀 6.63 英寸的屏幕尺寸下，有着 203 克的重量，和 8.8 毫米的厚度，谈不上轻薄。电池容量则为 4300 mAh，搭配 22.5W 的最大充电功率。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338457" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-09-1024x683.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-09-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-09-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-09-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-09.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>不过如果对比前代 4000mAh 电池，6.59 英寸屏幕重量为 206 克的荣耀 9X 之后，那么加了摄像头数量，加了 5G 元器件的荣耀 X10 在重量控制上是有进步的。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338454" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-06-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-06-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-06-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-06-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-06.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>熟悉的味道还有很多，比如侧边指纹的沿用。虽然更多的高端机喜欢用屏下指纹，但是单从解锁速度和效率来说，这个与电源键二合一的侧边指纹可以称得上是「快准稳」。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338450" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-02-1024x683.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-02-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-02-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-02.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>静止的画面体现不了的是荣耀 X10 的一个显着升级：90Hz 刷新率/180Hz 触控采样率屏幕。作为去年下半年至今手机行业最为显着的趋势之一，荣耀在一款起售价 2000 元以下的 5G 手机上用到高刷新率屏幕，基本也意味着，趋势渐成主流，今年在出货中坚机型上外要有高刷新率屏幕，内还得支持 5G，基础体验要看齐旗舰级。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338449" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-01-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-01-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-01-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-01-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-01.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>当然，支持 5G 这件事，一定要印在包装上。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338455" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-07-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-07-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-07-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-07-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-07.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>荣耀 X10 屏幕的从观感上看还不错，色彩亮度都没毛病。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338453" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-05-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-05-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-05-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-05-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-05.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>接下来我们把手机翻个面儿，介绍下荣耀强调过的背部玻璃工艺。</p>
<p>荣耀 X10 有四种配色：竞速蓝、探速黑，光速银，燃力橙。我们手上这款是竞速蓝。在光线的流转下，背部玻璃会呈现几何格子菱形的纹理，这当然是各种丝印和镀膜的结果。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338451" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-03-1024x683.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="683" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-03-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-03-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-03.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>具体来说，这块玻璃其实分为 21 层，从上到下依次是：AF 防指纹膜、玻璃 、logo 丝印、OCA 胶、渐变色胶印 6 层（渐变）、PET、UV 胶转印层（柱透镜纹理）、镀膜 5 层（炫光反光）、丝印盖底 4 层（油墨）。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338452" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-04-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-04-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-04-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-04-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-04.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>在拍照这块，荣耀 X10 主摄用到了华为和荣耀旗舰同款的 4000 万像素 RYYB 传感器，主打夜景，也支持 4K 延时摄影和 960 帧慢动作。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338458" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-10-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-10-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-10-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-10.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>荣耀 X10 的三摄排列也从之前的红绿灯升级为矩阵式。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338462" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-13-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-13-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-13-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-13-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-13.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>接口取舍上，荣耀 X10 依旧保留了 3.5mm 耳机接口（顶部），底部则是扬声器、卡槽和 Type-C 接口。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-1338460" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12-1024x576.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/X10-12.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>对于一款起售价 1899 元的 5G 手机来说，荣耀 X10 可以称得上是这个价格档位上的「水桶机」，整体非常均衡，找不到明显短板。麒麟 820 接棒麒麟 810，表现让人满意，90Hz 高刷新率屏幕的加入，也是能让用户体验升级的配置，电池容量和充电功率则是常规提升。</p>
<p>另外就是升降摄像头和侧边指纹的继承，虽然说现在的旗舰手机不太用这两个设计，但是从用户观感和体验上来说，他们和挖孔屏以及屏下指纹是各有千秋的功能点，是取是舍都不为错。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div id="ifanr_profile" style="border:1px solid #ccc;font-size:14px;margin:27px auto;font-family:Arial;">
